text:
Hey Ben! 

I’m alright! Yeah we did meet in London! 

I’ve been filming this weekend for my Final Major Project!

Nice! 

What’s the project? What techniques are you looking to develop and be able to show off once it’s done??

It’s pretty much someone walking down a few streets cutting between them with different transitions and I plan on doing some clean up, roto, incorporating 3D and a Matte Painting into a scene as well as a sky replacement. 

Pretty much to show off my comp skills.
